\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 Another thing that cheered us very much in our journey was the giving out tracts in French, which we got at Paris.  
