 not allow them to; be given in the streets, but in a house, or steam\_boat, or diligence, or for sale, they are lawful.  The people in every village crowded round us to receive them.  We felt that.  
this was doing what we could for France, and "sowing beside all waters."
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057 Another interesting thing was, that a Catholic priest travelled one whole night with us in the Diligence.  
